snippet.title: Aichi Emperors Zero - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the game on itch.io : https://aich.itch.io/emperors-zero

Aichi Emperors Zero is a third person cooperative motorbikes-fighting game, with a local multiplayer split-screen and developed for consoles.

You will personify japanese bikers attired in traditional costumes, perpetuating the samurai tradition. Through their epic story, these warriors from another time will have to engage with numerous opponents to eventually claim back their territory, the city of Yumeshima.
